description:
MpClusterHandling:  Records of MP Cluster Handling events, including timestamps, location, cell IDs, and associated equipment references.

dateTime: Timestamp of the MP Cluster Handling event.
Area_Name: Geographic area where the event occurred (e.g., NR_Balikpapan).
CellId:  Unique identifier of the cell where the event occurred.
Id2: Duplicate of CellId.
Id3:  An identifier, likely a sequential or categorical ID.
vsDataType: Data type identifier, indicating this record relates to MP Cluster Handling.
vsDataFormatVersion: Version of the data format used.
MpClusterHandling.mpClusterHandlingId: Unique ID for this specific MP Cluster Handling instance.
MpClusterHandling.primaryCoreRef:  Reference string identifying the primary core network equipment involved.
